Description: Up for sale is a very nice 1990 Rickenbacker 360 12-String guitar in rare White finish! Comes in the Original Case. Original parts and complete featuring Hi-Gain pickups for some killer classic raw Rick sound. Original tail piece replaced with easy to string black tail piece included. Original broken tail piece is included which you can mail back to Rickenbacker in to get original "R" tail piece if so desired. I just put new strings on and this one - it is a lot easier to re-string with this replacement tail piece. Includes extra set of new Rickenbacker flat wound strings. The guitar maintains its jaw-dropping physical beauty, and of course the one-of-a-kind Rickenbacker sound. Plays like butter. Upgraded 12 string bridge (installed by Mandolin Bro)with 12 separate bridge pieces for perfect intonation all up the neck. It has that famous chimey jingle-jangle - bright and alive. Nothing quite sounds like a Rick! It sounds so GREAT amplified so when you start playing it you won't be able to stop. Unsurpassed for its tone variations. Just an incredible guitar! This guitar is in Very Good cosmetic condition! Showing very light play wear, small scratches, very minor dents to speak of. The neck is perfect. The action is NICE and low with no string buzz. The original frets show only minimal wear.
Title: Rickenbacker 360 12-String 1990 WHITE Very Good Condition
